## 4. 변경 상세 설계

### 4.1 Backend

#### CookieProperties (신규)

```java
// common/security/CookieProperties.java
@Component
public class CookieProperties {
    @Value("${app.cookie.secure:false}")
    private boolean secure;

    public void addAuthCookie(HttpServletResponse response, String value, int maxAge) {
        String cookie = String.format(
            "trmdict_token=%s; HttpOnly; Path=/api; Max-Age=%d; SameSite=Strict%s",
            value, maxAge, secure ? "; Secure" : ""
        );
        response.addHeader("Set-Cookie", cookie);
    }

    public void clearAuthCookie(HttpServletResponse response) {
        addAuthCookie(response, "", 0);
    }
}
```

> **`javax.servlet.http.Cookie`는 SameSite 미지원 (Java 8 한계)** → `Set-Cookie` 헤더 직접 작성으로 해결.

#### JwtAuthenticationFilter 변경 포인트

```java
// 변경 전: Authorization 헤더에서 추출
String header = req.getHeader("Authorization");
if (header != null && header.startsWith("Bearer ")) {
    token = header.substring(7);
}

// 변경 후: 쿠키에서 추출
private static final String COOKIE_NAME = "trmdict_token";

Cookie[] cookies = req.getCookies();
if (cookies != null) {
    for (Cookie c : cookies) {
        if (COOKIE_NAME.equals(c.getName())) {
            token = c.getValue();
            break;
        }
    }
}
```

#### AuthController 변경 포인트

```java
// POST /login: 응답 body에서 accessToken 제거, 쿠키 발급
@PostMapping("/login")
public ApiResponse<LoginResponse> login(
        @Valid @RequestBody LoginDto dto, HttpServletResponse response) {
    AuthService.LoginResult result = authService.login(dto.getUsername(), dto.getPassword());
    cookieProperties.addAuthCookie(response, result.getAccessToken(), (int) result.getExpiresIn());
    AuthUserVo u = result.getUser();
    return ApiResponse.success(new LoginResponse(
            new UserSummary(u.getId(), u.getUsername(), u.getName(), u.getRole())
    ));
}

// POST /logout: 신규 엔드포인트
@PostMapping("/logout")
public ApiResponse<Void> logout(HttpServletResponse response) {
    cookieProperties.clearAuthCookie(response);
    return ApiResponse.success(null);
}
```

#### application yml 추가

```yaml
# application-local.yml
app:
  cookie:
    secure: false

# application-prod.yml
app:
  cookie:
    secure: true
```

#### SecurityConfig — `permitAll` 추가

```java
.antMatchers("/api/v1/auth/login", "/api/v1/auth/logout").permitAll()
```

